title: Will google charge for the existing Original Quality photo after 1st Feb 2022? I am using Pixel 3XL
content: I am using Pixel 3XL, the photos i uploaded from my device to Google Photos are in Original Quality. The Google Photos storage policy change will be effective 1st Feb 2022 for my device. For the Original Quality photos i have uploaded before 1st Feb 2022, will they still be accessible and will it count to my 15GB free storage?
